name: PROPERTIES 00 - Terrain in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood. 
This large flattened land has authorization for the construction of a business or home. 
It has low cost taxes and its unique location in front of the main square allows walks with your cat friend to be more fun and frequent. 
Land measurements: 50m x 60m.
